Wednesday, February 9, 1994

MERIT DOCKET

93-2572. Jones v. Reda.

In Mandamus. On motion for summary judgment. Motion treated as motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Mover, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
